      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Handle 'dispute' → Forward API\n\nPOST https://api.example.com/v1/records — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Consolidate Handling · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API",
